<P>
GIVE UP GUNS? 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I pose this question to National Rifle Assn. members and their supporters: If 
you could save one child's life, would you give up your guns? 
</P>
<P>
 ROBERT L. FOX 
</P>
<P>
 Los Angeles 
