<HEADLINE>
<P>
WORLD CUP USA '94 / THE FIRST ROUND; SPOTLIGHT; KEEP GOING 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By LISA DILLMAN 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Who has the worst job at the Rose Bowl? 
</P>
<P>
 An early candidate was the poor soul sweltering in the pink bunny suit, 
beating a drum while walking the grounds in the afternoon heat Sunday. 
</P>
<P>
 The Energizer bunny and soccer -- who would have thought it? 
</P>
<P>
 "Twenty minutes outside and 20 minutes inside the entertainment center," said 
the bunny's minder. "There's been no problems. Oh, yeah, except for little kids 
grabbing his tail." LISA DILLMAN 
</P>
</TEXT>
