<TEXT>
<P>
 A man who allegedly waved an 11-inch fillet knife at his wife and threatened 
to kill her just as "O.J. Simpson did to his wife" pleaded not guilty to one 
misdemeanor count of assault, police said. 
</P>
<P>
 Seppo Gujani Virtanen, 46, who was held in Glendale City Jail in lieu of 
